quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  18,88,"Ṣùgbọ́n ní ti ẹni tí ó bá gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí ó sì ṣe iṣẹ́ rere, tirẹ̀ ni ẹ̀san rere. A ó sì sọ̀rọ̀ ìrọ̀rùn fún un nínú àṣẹ Wa.”"
  18,89,"Lẹ́yìn náà, ó mú ọ̀nà kan tọ̀"
  18,90,"títí ó fi dé ibùyọ òòrùn ayé. Ó rí i tí ń yọ lórí àwọn ènìyàn kan, tí A kò fún ní gàgá (ààbò) kan níbi òòrùn."
  19,49,"Nígbà tí ó yẹra fún àwọn àti n̄ǹkan tí wọ́n ń jọ́sìn fún lẹ́yìn Allāhu, A sì ta á lọ́rẹ (ọmọ), ’Ishāƙ àti Ya‘ƙūb (ọmọọmọ rẹ̀). A sì ṣe ọ̀kọ̀ọ̀kan wọn ní Ànábì.1 {1}",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah Hūd;  11:71.]
  19,50,"Àti pé A ta wọ́n lọ́rẹ láti inú ìkẹ́ Wa. A sì fi òdodo sórí ahọ́n gbogbo àwọn ènìyàn nìpa wọn (ìyẹn ni pé, gbogbo ìjọ ẹlẹ́sìn ló ń sọ̀rọ̀ wọn ní dáadáa)."
  19,51,"Sọ ìtàn (Ànábì) Mūsā tí ó wà nínú al-Ƙur’ān. Dájúdájú ó jẹ́ ẹni-ẹ̀ṣà, ó jẹ́ Òjíṣẹ́, (ó tún jẹ́) Ànábì."
  20,31,"Fi kún mi lọ́wọ́."
  20,32,"Fi ṣakẹgbẹ́ mi nínú iṣẹ́ mi"
  20,33,"torí kí á lè ṣàfọ̀mọ́ (orúkọ) Rẹ ní ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀,"
  21,7,"A kò rán ẹnì kan ní iṣẹ́-òjíṣẹ́ ṣíwájú rẹ àfi àwọn ọkùnrin tí À ń fi ìmísí ránṣẹ́ sí. Nítorí náà, ẹ bèèrè lọ́dọ̀ àwọn oníràn-ántí tí ẹ̀yin kò bá mọ̀.1 {1}",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah Yūsuf: 12:109 àti sūrah an-Nahl; 16:43.]
  21,8,"A kò sì ṣe wọ́n ní abara tí kì í jẹun. Wọn kò sì jẹ́ olùṣegbére (nílé ayé).1 {1}",1:[Àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ pé Ànábì ‘Īsā ọmọ Mọryam - kí ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - ti kú sọ pé, “Āyah yìí àti āyah 21:34 níwájú tako àì tí ì kú Ànábì ‘Īsā títí di àkókò yìí àti títí di àkókò òpin ayé. Nítorí náà, Ànábì ‘Īsā - kí ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - ti kú”.]
  21,9,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A mú àdéhùn Wa ṣẹ fún wọn. A sì gba àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ àti àwọn tí A bá fẹ́ là. A sì pa àwọn olùtayọ ẹnu-ààlà run."